<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <title>Actividades</title>
  </head>
    <body>
      <main>
      <a href='@Url.Action("CrearEvento", "Home")'>Crear Actividad</a>
        <section>
          <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide">
          <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide-to="0"
              class="active"
              aria-current="true"
              aria-label="Slide 1"
            ></button>
            <button
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide-to="1"
              aria-label="Slide 2"
            ></button>
            <button
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide-to="2"
              aria-label="Slide 3"
            ></button>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <img src="./img/ManosCreativas.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." />
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5>Manos creativas</h5>
                <p> Taller de manualidades donde los abuelos crean objetos con papel, lana o pintura, estimulando su creatividad y coordinación</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img src="./img/MoverseConAlegria.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." />
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5> Moverse con alegría</h5>
                <p>Clases de ejercicios suaves para mejorar la movilidad, el equilibrio y mantenerse activos de forma divertida.</p>
                <a href='@Url.Action("DesInscribirse", "Home")'>//depende si inscribirse o desinscribirse eso tiene que ser un bool de cada actividad</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img src="./img/SaboresConHistoria.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." />
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                <h5> Sabores con historia</h5>
                <p> Taller de cocina donde preparan recetas tradicionales o nuevas, compartiendo saberes y experiencias.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
            <button
              class="carousel-control-prev"
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide="prev"
            >
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button
              class="carousel-control-next"
              type="button"
              data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
              data-bs-slide="next"
            >
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <script
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
          ></script> 
        </section>
      </main>
  </body>
</html>
